Jon Matonis is an e-money researcher and crypto economist focused on expanding the circulation of non-political digital currencies. His career has included senior influential posts at Sumitomo Bank, Visa, VeriSign, and Hushmail. Currently, he is Executive Director of the [[Bitcoin_Foundation]] and also serves on its board. He is also a Contributing Editor of the digital currency news publication [[CoinDesk]].

